Sends a private message to a particular person. 

Usage:
  tell <person> <message>

<person> is case sensitive

If Joe types:
  tell Jack Hi!
  
Player Jack sees:
  Joe tells you: Hi!

See also: [help]reply[/help]
See also: [help]say[/help]
